title: Camilla Hamids bakresa: Marocko
overview: Come along to Camilla's Moroccan family where she gets to learn about the Moroccan baking culture together to understand more about where she belongs. Camilla has always felt too Swedish in Morocco and too Moroccan in Sweden and never really felt 100% at home anywhere. With this program, she hopes not only to offer new exciting baking pleasure, but also understanding and recognition.
